{"title":"俺来唱唱白舍楞（柳琴书）","authors":["张新田　董玉屿"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺来唱唱白舍楞（柳琴书）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包头钢铁公司　张新田　董玉屿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿山生产掀高潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好人好事真不少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺来唱唱白舍楞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面红旗铁矿飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想红来干劲高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产当中是英豪哇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六○年一月间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻机的天轮不能转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六级大风拼命地刮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刮得钻机直打颤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他顶风冒险上大架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修好钻机保生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个午夜风雪天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟班钻机修转盘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修了半天没修好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急得大家打转转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老白闻听忙赶到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮助他们检修完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白舍楞不简单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤俭节约是模范。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴油来一度电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毫不浪费细盘算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦奋斗八年整，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设祖国把力量添。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年五月一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄来到北京城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多年的心愿得实现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舍楞见到了毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福的眼泪往外流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领袖的教导记心里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白舍楞回矿山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象猛虎把翼添，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导全组闹革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们实现了千米钻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千米钻威力大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保证矿山多增产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说老白，唱老白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老白的干劲哪里来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧主的鞭痕他不忘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的恩情记心怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇到困难学主席著作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劲如泉涌干起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老白的事迹不平凡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怪俺自己文化浅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编不全来唱不好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望大家提意见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱到此处算一段，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请到矿山去看看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《包钢报》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}